<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sessão Expirada - Territory Manager</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #121212; color: #E0E0E0; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .card { background-color: #1E1E1E; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2.5rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
    <div class="card w-full max-w-lg shadow-2xl text-center border border-gray-800">
        <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-user-lock text-blue-500 text-4xl"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Sessão Expirada</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Sua autenticação expirou ou você não está logado. Por favor, entre novamente para continuar.</p>

        <a href="/v1/dashboard/login" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all active:scale-95">
            <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt mr-2"></i>Ir para Login
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>